    "instruction": "Filter trace.csv to the incident window (start = '2024-01-23 15:11:51 UTC', end = '2024-01-23 15:41:51 UTC'). Then restrict to trace_name values that indicate calls between candidate services: those containing any of the substrings 'to_ts-order-service', 'to_ts-auth-service', 'to_ts-route-service', 'to_ts-travel-service', 'from_ts-order-service', 'from_ts-auth-service', 'from_ts-route-service', or 'from_ts-travel-service'. For each (cmdb_id, trace_name) group, compute compact aggregates: count, mean(value), max(value), min(value), and earliest timestamp (min timestamp) within the window. Return up to top 20 groups sorted by count descending. Include columns: cmdb_id, trace_name, count, earliest_timestamp (UTC), min_value, mean_value, max_value. If no matching traces are found, explicitly state that." }

